@startuml
title Activity Diagram - Submit Assignment

start

note right
Steps:
1. Student opens assignment page
2. Student uploads work
3. System validates deadline and file rules
4. If valid, system stores submission
5. System shows receipt OR submission error message
end note

:Open Assignment Page;
:Upload Work;
:Validate Deadline and File Rules;

if (Submission valid?) then (Yes)
  :Store Submission;
  :Show Submission Receipt;
else (No)
  :Show Submission Error;
  :Request Re-upload;
endif

stop
@enduml
